    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>Manages multiple world recordings and provides a simple interface for recording operations.

This manager handles the lifecycle of recordings, including starting, stopping,
saving, and listing recordings. It manages a single active recorder at a time.
</verbatim> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
